sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Admin
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant Fetcher as Manifest Fetcher
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Reconciler as Component Reconciler
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation and Component Deployment

    User->>API: Create DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: OpenShift OAuth
    API->>Webhook: POST /validate-*<br/>mTLS (API Server cert)
    Webhook-->>API: Validation Response
    API-->>User: CR Created

    Note over DSCCtrl: Watch event triggered

    DSCCtrl->>API: Get DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>DSCCtrl: CR Details

    DSCCtrl->>Fetcher: Fetch component manifests
    Fetcher->>GitHub: GET /repos/.../manifests<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    GitHub-->>Fetcher: Kustomize Manifests
    Fetcher-->>DSCCtrl: Manifests

    DSCCtrl->>Reconciler: Deploy component
    Reconciler->>API: Create/Update Resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Reconciler: Resources Created
    Reconciler-->>DSCCtrl: Deployment Complete

    DSCCtrl->>API: Update DSC Status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>DSCCtrl: Status Updated

    DSCCtrl->>API: Create FeatureTracker CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>DSCCtrl: FeatureTracker Created

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 2: Component Monitoring

    Prom->>DSCCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    DSCCtrl-->>Prom: Prometheus Metrics

    Prom->>API: GET Component Metrics<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Prom: Component Health Data

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: Secret and Certificate Generation

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over DSCCtrl: DSCInitialization Reconciliation
        DSCCtrl->>API: Create SecretGenerator CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        API-->>DSCCtrl: Secret Created

        DSCCtrl->>API: Get OpenShift Proxy Config<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        API-->>DSCCtrl: CA Bundle

        DSCCtrl->>API: Create odh-trusted-ca-bundle ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        API-->>DSCCtrl: ConfigMap Created

        DSCCtrl->>API: Distribute to Component Namespaces<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        API-->>DSCCtrl: Distribution Complete
    end
